.TH "nvme_init_fdp_reclaim_unit_handle_update" 9 "nvme_init_fdp_reclaim_unit_handle_update" "April 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nvme_init_fdp_reclaim_unit_handle_update \- Initialize passthru command to update a list of reclaim unit handles
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" nvme_init_fdp_reclaim_unit_handle_update
.BI "(struct libnvme_passthru_cmd *cmd "  ","
.BI "__u32 nsid "  ","
.BI "void *pids "  ","
.BI "unsigned int npids "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "cmd" 12
Passthru command to use
.IP "nsid" 12
Namespace identifier
.IP "pids" 12
List of placement identifiers buffer
.IP "npids" 12
Number of placement identifiers
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Initializes the passthru command buffer for the I/O Management Send -
Reclaim Unit Handle Update command.
